🚀 Installation
1. Install dependencies
npm install


Faster than the time it takes to decide whether you should run the testnet or not.

2. Add accounts

Open the file accounts.txt, one private key per line:

0xabc123...your_private_key_1
0xdef456...your_private_key_2

3. (Optional) Add proxies

Open the file proxy.txt, one proxy per line:

host:port
host:port:username:password
http://username:password@host:port
socks5://username:password@host:port

4. Run the bot
npm start

⚙️ Configuration

All configuration settings are stored in config.json.
This file will be automatically generated on the first run.

{
  // Number of parallel processing threads
  "threads": 10,

  // Random delay between actions (ms) — simulates human behavior
  "delay": {
    "min": 3000,
    "max": 7000
  },

  // Enable/disable individual features
  "features": {
    "claimShelbyUSD": true,    // Claim ShelbyUSD test tokens
    "claimAPT": true,          // Claim APT test tokens
    "uploadFiles": true,       // Upload files to storage
    "autoGenerateFiles": true  // Automatically generate random files
  },

  // Upload configuration
  "upload": {
    "totalFiles": 30,          // Total files to upload per wallet
    "daysSpread": 5,           // Spread uploads across N days
    "filesPerSession": 6,      // Files uploaded per session
    "expirationDays": 30,      // Blob storage duration
    "maxFileSizeKB": 500,      // Maximum file size (KB)
    "minFileSizeKB": 1,        // Minimum file size (KB)
    "fileTypes": ["png", "jpg", "pdf", "txt", "json", "csv"]
  },

  "proxy": {
    "enabled": false,
    "rotatePerAccount": true   // Rotate proxy per account
  },

  // Faucet configuration
  "faucet": {
    "aptAmount": 100000000,    // 1 APT (8 decimals)
    "shelbyUsdAmount": 1000000000,
    "retryAttempts": 3,
    "retryDelay": 5000
  },

  // Automation cycle
  "cycle": {
    "enabled": true,           // Enable automatic looping
    "intervalHours": 24,       // Wait time between cycles
    "maxCycles": 0             // 0 = unlimited (runs indefinitely)
  }
}
